quran[12{c,v,t}:
25,56,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum ko to hum ne bas aik Mubasher aur Nazeer bana kar bheja hai"
25,57,"inn se keh do ke"" mein is kaam par tum se koi aُjrt nahi mangta, meri aُjrt bas yahi hai ke jis ka jee chahay woh apne rab ka rasta ikhtiyar kar le """
25,58,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, uss khuda par bharosa rakho jo zindah hai aur kabhi marnay wala nahi is ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh karo apne bundon ke gunaaho se bas usi ka bakhabar hona kaafi hai"
25,59,"woh jis ne chay dinon mein zameen aur aasman ko aur unn saari cheezon ko bana kar rakh diya jo aasman o zameen ke darmain hain, phir aap hi ( kaayenaat ke takhat saltanat )"" arsh"" par jalva farma howa rehman, is ki shaan bas kisi jan-nay walay se pucho"
25,60,"inn logon se jab kaha jata hai ke is Rehman ko sajda karo to kehte hain"" Rehman kya hota hai? kya bas jisay to keh day isi ko hum sajda karte phiren ?"" yeh dawat un ki nafrat mein ulta aur izafah kar deti hai"
25,61,bara mutbarrik hai woh jis ne aasman mein burj banaye aur is mein aik chairag aur aik chamakta chaand roshan kya
25,62,"wohi hai jis ne raat aur din ko aik dosray ka janasheen banaya, har is shakhs ke liye jo sabaq lena chahay, ya shukar guzaar hona chahay"
25,63,Rehman ke ( asli ) bande woh hain jo zameen par naram chaal chaltay hain aur jaahil un ke mun ko ayen to keh dete hain ke tum ko salam
25,64,jo apne rab ke huzoor sjday aur qiyam mein raatain guzartay hain
25,65,"jo duayen karte hain ke"" ae hamaray rab, jahannum ke azaab se hum ko bacha le, uss ka azaab to jaan ka laago hai"
25,66,"woh bara hi bura mstqr aur maqam hai """
25,67,"jo kharch karte hain to nah fuzool kharchi karte hain nah bukhal, balkay un ka kharch dono ant_haon ke darmain aitdaal par qaim rehta hai"
